schools.name: Don R Daniel Ninth Grade Campus

data.description: This beautiful one story home that sits on just over one acre in highly sought Aledo isd is ready for its next family.  This home features a grand open design from the spacious kitchen and nook area into the oversized family room.  The split floor plan provides privacy for the family and guests. The game room off the family room is great for the kids or a large study.  Enjoy the large back patio with fireplace looking out to the fenced backyard. The home is equipped with security cameras and a water softener. Bring your buyers for this incredible opportunity.
